snippet.title: Mario Party Star Rush - Debut Gameplay - Nintendo E3 2016
snippet.description:
Nintendo Treehouse: Live @ E3 2016. It's always your turn in Mario Party Star Rush, a non-stop party coming to the Nintendo 3DS. Check out this all-new Mario Party experience straight from E3 2016.

Check out more information here! http://e3.nintendo.com/games/mario-party-star-rush-3ds
